title: Ravenna Park Studio
posting_body: ['Available September 1', 'Very roomy, clean, light-filled studio apartment in the Ravenna neighborhood.', ' It is big and bright with good size spaces.', ' Check out the extra-large closet & big laundry room/storage.', 'Kitchen has good counter space, plenty of cabinets, range/oven, dishwasher, disposal and breakfast bar open to living area.', 'PHOTOS ARE FROM VACANT UNIT.', ' CURRENTLY OCCUPIED.', 'The apartment is located about ¼ miles north of Ravenna/Cowen Park in a quiet charming neighborhood.', '  Easy biking distance to UW campus and to bus lines to everywhere.', ' The neighborhood is populated with nice restaurants, shops and has a walk score of 95.', ' Close to shopping, freeway access and transportation to downtown Seattle.', ' A great location!', '•\tOn-site covered parking assigned', '•\tSecured building, with intercom entry', '•\tWasher and dryer located inside the unit', 'One-year lease.', 'Written minimum rental criteria, available by request and posted in the unit, includes adequate income, references, and credit.', 'No sight-unseen applications accepted.', '$45 application fee per person.', '$1050 deposits.', 'Tenant pays addl $90 p/person for water/garbage and all electric utilities + $10 covered parking fee.', 'No smoking.', 'No Pets.', 'Electronic payment method assumed.', 'Due to very cooperative tenant, all showings are by appointment.', 'Call for available times.', 'Steve', 'show contact info']
